A fan has taken a handshake too far after making an awkward demand fromTiwa Savage. The incident stems from a recent video encounter showing Wizkid spanking the mother of one’s bum. Inspired by that act, a fan has asked if he can spank the musician’s bum. The naughty fan took to Twitter and wrote: “Mama j, can I spank ur ass?🙈” However, Tiwa didn’t take offence even though the demand was offensive. Replying the fan, she wrote: “Yeah sure. Everyone has one, nothing special about mine, na mess you go find there sha 🤷🏼‍♀️” Source